<h1>👍 Booking confirmation 👍</h1>

<h2>Hi <%= @booking.user.user_contact.first_name.capitalize %> <%= @booking.user.user_contact.last_name.capitalize %></h2>

<p>Your booking for <%= @booking.flat.name %> has been confirmed by the landlord <%= @booking.flat.user.user_contact.first_name.capitalize %> <%= @booking.flat.user.user_contact.last_name.capitalize %>:</p>

<%= cl_image_tag @booking.flat.photo.key , height: 300, width: 400, crop: :fill %>

<br>
<p>📆 Sart date: <%= @booking.start_date %></p>
<p>📅 End date: <%= @booking.end_date %></p>
<% night_number = @booking.end_date - @booking.start_date %>
<br>
<p>🌙 For <%= @booking.guest_count %> persons</p>

<p>------------------------</p>
<p>TOTAL: <%= @booking.flat.price_per_night * night_number.to_i %> €</p>
<br>

<h3>To finish your booking you can proceed to the payment on our website.</h3>

<%= link_to "Pay now", booking_url(@booking), class:"btn btn-cards" %>

<br>
Thanks for joining our service! Please check back often.
